.TH "batadv_v_iface_update_mac" 9 "batadv_v_iface_update_mac" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
batadv_v_iface_update_mac \- react to hard-interface MAC address change
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" batadv_v_iface_update_mac
.BI "(struct batadv_hard_iface *hard_iface "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "hard_iface" 12
the modified interface
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
If the modified interface is the primary one, update the originator
address in the ELP and OGM messages to reflect the new MAC address.
